<lb n="0787b02" ed="X"/><lb n="0206a08" ed="R126"/><cb:juan n="003" fun="close"><cb:jhead>會稽雲門湛然澄禪師語錄卷第三</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>